pageItems.description:
• Recommended for contractors using a non-WEC device that need to connect to a standard WEC corporate workstation.
• ETA for turnaround: 7 business days from date of approval.
• All VDIs use Windows and are created in the CORP domain.
• A VDI is assigned to a single person and is dedicated to that person only.  Each person who needs access to a VDI should be provided their own unique VDI.
• If you are requesting multiple VDIs, a separate request is required for each person needing a VDI.
• VDIs will be automatically retired after 90 days of non-use.

*Disclaimer: based on your responses to the form questions, you will be automatically recommended the type of VDI you require or hosted apps if you don't require VDI functionality.
